name: Sakurajima Mai (樱岛麻衣/桜島麻衣) LoRA
description:
Sakurajima Mai from Rascal Does Not Dream of Bunny Girl Senpai series.

To avoid interference with other LoRA models (also the ability to change her appearance), this model is set with several trigger words:

  • For Mai herself, use black hair, long hair, hairclip only is enough, rabbit hair ornamentalso helps;

  • For her school uniform costume, add the following prompts to the base prompt: school uniform, blazer, red necktie, pantyhose

  • For bunny costume: playboy bunny, rabbit ears, black bowtie, pantyhose, fake animal ears
